@startuml
title Load Profile - Clean Architecture Sequence
hide footbox
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor Researcher
boundary UpdateProfileView
control LoadProfileController
participant LoadProfileInputBoundary <<boundary>>
control LoadProfileInteractor
participant LoadProfileDataAccessInterface <<boundary>>
entity ServerRepository
collections "ScholarMatch API" as Server
participant LoadProfileOutputBoundary <<boundary>>
control LoadProfilePresenter
entity LoadProfileViewModel

Researcher -> UpdateProfileView: Open profile editor
UpdateProfileView -> LoadProfileController: execute()
LoadProfileController -> LoadProfileInputBoundary: execute()
LoadProfileInputBoundary -> LoadProfileInteractor: execute()
LoadProfileInteractor -> LoadProfileDataAccessInterface: getProfile()
LoadProfileDataAccessInterface -> ServerRepository: getProfile()
ServerRepository -> Server: GET /api/profile
Server --> ServerRepository: profile JSON
ServerRepository --> LoadProfileInteractor: User
LoadProfileInteractor -> LoadProfileOutputBoundary: prepareSuccessView(outputData)
LoadProfileOutputBoundary -> LoadProfilePresenter: prepareSuccessView(outputData)
LoadProfilePresenter -> LoadProfileViewModel: setProfile(profile)
LoadProfileViewModel --> UpdateProfileView: notify change
UpdateProfileView --> Researcher: Show pre-filled form

note over LoadProfileController, LoadProfileOutputBoundary
Use-case contracts do not depend on Swing, HTTP, or JSON.
end note
@enduml
